{"tid":1144893,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇wall street苦主","createTime":"2019-05-08T10:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T12:20:20.000Z","uid":218353,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"84129f0c6cc00eabce1fee9dd09830b491f34133","tid":1144893,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"喺度講聲先: 如果你想報呢間野就最好諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年前左右簽咗約， 上咗兩個月左右覺得唔對路就想走， 但係佢會係咁唔畀你走， 話讀完先有得走， 或者係講啲鼓勵你嘅說話等你唔好走， 不斷咁話你讀完先有得走， 咁我又真係聽咗佢講讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 知自己戇鳩， 到今年3月左右讀完， 嗰陣上去再話quit, 佢就同我講話因為我讀曬佢哋啲課程所以冇得quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 依家冇再去,因為去到都係戇鳩鳩咁坐喺度 ，唔想交錢畀佢哋， 雖然簽咗合約最後都係要交錢, 但係唔想佢哋追數追得咁輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主旨:佢哋一開始會用盡所有手法去引誘你簽佢哋份合約， 佢哋啲合約條款多到仆街， 全部都係對佢哋有利嘅陳述， 如果你讀到一半 發覺唔對路想走真係唔係咁易<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇苦主有相同經歷？ 可唔可以分享下點樣走咗條數或者佢哋會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家爭佢哋八千蚊到， 就係唔想畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 明明已經同佢哋講咗話唔再去唔用佢哋服務， 但係佢哋都會夾硬叫你交錢畀佢交到份合約完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e0996abd83b630367b56cc2550fc4c4dc698f4","tid":1144893,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"幾錢先, 你唔俾佢可以告你？"},{"pid":"47d92b0b7e9ea48d95dde95d008872fde31d2cf9","tid":1144893,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e0996abd83b630367b56cc2550fc4c4dc698f4","tid":1144893,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"幾錢先, 你唔俾佢可以告你？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"成份約加埋要交三萬蚊左右， 依家交咗二萬多啲， 淨低我真係唔會再去所以唔想畀， 依家上嚟問下睇下有冇類似經歷嘅人可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會唔會告我， 問過議員話小額錢債一般都唔會理"},{"pid":"adaf5dc8a391a2be9a527650f011900a306eb1e8","tid":1144893,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"點會唔比走 <br />\n讀晒你啲時間就已經完左啦"},{"pid":"fa5d6d5a7adacc303dfd2a77ee4ccaff1d8b0d20","tid":1144893,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adaf5dc8a391a2be9a527650f011900a306eb1e8","tid":1144893,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"點會唔比走 <br />\n讀晒你啲時間就已經完左啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"佢依家係都要話我爭佢錢， 話一定要交埋啲尾數先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明一般呢啲只要唔去就唔使交錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90c057bcfac6c4115b2369d6e162fb255cf5d85","tid":1144893,"uid":247508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"係咪讀英文果間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cd9ea9d8a7c49b80a2e5d29a5b186516a99845","tid":1144893,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"推~<br />\n<br />\n求相同經歷巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc55661e515ebed7174f4b731dc6e4f7a01ff22","tid":1144893,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90c057bcfac6c4115b2369d6e162fb255cf5d85","tid":1144893,"uid":247508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"係咪讀英文果間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,